            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"地產｜恒地九龍城南首加推28伙 折實售643萬起\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"502\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/La7gZ15XzW1pdZUwE2YseQ--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTUwMg--/https://media.zenfs.com/ko/fortune_insight_694/dbddec0f78d2a1ab4bc25a6950c04ffb\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">地產｜恒地九龍城南首加推28伙 折實售643萬起</figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">恒地(00012)九龍城南角道項目南首上載全新價單，加推28伙，折實售價643萬元起。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">是次加推28伙，包括22伙一房戶及6伙兩房戶，實用面積258至351平方呎，價單定價由643.2萬至923.9萬元，價單呎價由24456至26322元，扣除最高2%折扣，折實售價由630.33萬至905.42萬元，折實呎價由23967至25795元。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">項目同日定於下周一(6日)以價單形式推售17伙一房戶及5伙兩房戶，實用面積由258至351方呎，價單定價由 643.2萬至906.2萬元，價單呎價由24456至26307元，扣除最高2%折扣，折實售價由630.33萬至888.07萬元，折實呎價由23967至25781元。</p></div>",
